 la loi organique relative aux lois de finances'', [[La Documentation Fran\u00e7aise]], 2005, {{ISBN|2-11-005944-3}}\n** Independent administrative authorities\n*** [[Council of State (France)|Conseil d'\u00c9tat]], rapport public 2001, ''Les autorit\u00e9s administratives ind\u00e9pendantes'' (PDF) {{ISBN|2-11-004788-7}}\n\n==Further reading==\n* Fr\u00e9d\u00e9ric Monera, ''L'id\u00e9e de R\u00e9publique et la jurisprudence du Conseil constitutionnel'' - Paris: L.G.D.J., 2004 [http://www.fnac.com/Shelf/article.asp?PRID=1601897&Mn=2&Ra=-1&To=0&Nu=2&Fr=3]-[https://web.archive.org/web/20060923201826/http://www.lgdj.fr/rech_rapide.php?_Sess=c22f5de9dee93f9554d169596caad970&_Mots=monera&_TypeCode=]\n\n==External links==\n* [http://www.service-public.fr ''Service Public'', Official portal to public services] {{in lang|fr}}\n\n{{French Government}}\n{{Politics of Europe}}\n{{France topics}}\n\n[[Category:Politics of France|*]]\n", "name_user": "65.34.130.157", "label": "vandal", "comment": "", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Politics_of_France"}
